{"tid":972543,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒：摩連奴散步偶遇球迷，聆聽球迷談論戰術 E-mail 此主題給朋友","createTime":"2019-01-07T12:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T12:32:23.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf7333e8a17821f9948675f02e349d1d155c0ca","tid":972543,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/b947a1/f/800x0/https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/NINTCHDBPICT000459722648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fb947a1%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FNINTCHDBPICT000459722648.jpg&h=8d96deed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1月6日訊 <br />\n<br />\n雖然穆里尼奧已經離開了曼聯，但他的動向仍是媒體關注的焦點。近期《太陽報》抓拍到一幕有趣的畫面，穆里尼奧在散步期間與一位球迷相遇，兩人交談了很長時間，球迷似乎向穆帥闡述了自己的戰術觀點。<br />\n<br />\n當時穆里尼奧衣著休閒，正在倫敦家附近的街道上散步，突然被一位球迷打斷。兩人短暫握手後，球迷開始了長篇大論。<br />\n<br />\n這位球迷顯得情緒十分激動，不時做著手勢，似乎在闡釋他的足球戰術理念。<br />\n<br />\n據《太陽報》觀察，穆里尼奧表現得有一點驚訝，兩人交談結束後，他的表情有些無奈。聖誕節結束後，穆里尼奧就從葡萄牙返回，居住在西倫敦的家中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/sport/football/8125247/jose-mourinho-tactical-tips-london-manchester-united/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2F8125247%2Fjose-mourinho-tactical-tips-london-manchester-united%2F&d=OQn54MhRhb3uFRN17xZq%2FpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1762cf8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thesun.co.uk/sport/football/8125247/jose-mourinho-tactical-tips-london-manchester-united/</a><br />\n<br />\n就先休息一年吧   一年後  我要看到你再度重出江湖   引領風騷   教練   YO <img src=\"https://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/littledd/DD_sunglasses.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Flittledd%2FDD_sunglasses.gif&h=e0f83c09&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}